It's impossible

300
00:31:04,975 --> 00:31:06,824
I draw it by myself

301
00:31:07,024 --> 00:31:09,123
There's no second one

302
00:31:12,734 --> 00:31:13,915
It's useless to talk this with me

303
00:31:26,238 --> 00:31:27,303
It's him

304
00:31:27,503 --> 00:31:29,860
Gu Yishan,right?

305
00:31:37,515 --> 00:31:38,398
Student

306
00:31:44,949 --> 00:31:46,608
Xiang Zeyi,where were you

307
00:31:46,808 --> 00:31:50,809
Gu Yishan took your works to the press
Go explain to them

308
00:31:51,009 --> 00:31:54,296
-Where is he
-I don't know

309
00:31:54,496 --> 00:31:55,431
Where is he

310
00:31:57,537 --> 00:31:58,370
I don't know

311
00:32:01,257 --> 00:32:03,633
He often goes to the snack street

312
00:32:03,833 --> 00:32:06,307
Xiang Zeyi

313
00:32:24,791 --> 00:32:29,361
Xiang Zeyi

314
00:32:45,939 --> 00:32:49,536
Should I call you thief now

315
00:32:49,736 --> 00:32:55,448
What are you doing
Let go of me

316
00:32:55,648 --> 00:32:57,944
What

317
00:32:58,144 --> 00:33:00,441
Don't move

318
00:33:09,363 --> 00:33:14,616
This is my first time to see how reasonable a thief is

319
00:33:14,816 --> 00:33:16,179
What

320
00:33:22,811 --> 00:33:25,399
Hit him

321
00:34:13,914 --> 00:34:19,898
Listen,those drawings are already mine

322
00:34:20,098 --> 00:34:23,253
and will always be mine

323
00:34:27,702 --> 00:34:28,304
Let's go

324
00:34:28,504 --> 00:34:31,565
Stupid

325
00:36:55,981 --> 00:36:57,114
Dada,any news

326
00:36:57,314 --> 00:36:59,515
No,we can't contact him

327
00:36:59,715 --> 00:37:01,534
How does the college say

328
00:37:01,734 --> 00:37:06,407
They don't know either

329
00:37:06,607 --> 00:37:09,095
How's that possible

330
00:37:09,295 --> 00:37:12,447
It's been a week

331
00:37:12,647 --> 00:37:14,595
How can anyone disappear like this

332
00:37:14,795 --> 00:37:18,851
Ye Zi,if there's any news,
I will inform you immediately

333
00:37:23,462 --> 00:37:24,505
Don't be upset

334
00:37:24,705 --> 00:37:26,235
I will try my best to find him

335
00:37:40,340 --> 00:37:42,266
What are you watching

336
00:37:46,605 --> 00:37:47,830
You are looking for Xiang Zeyi

337
00:37:49,510 --> 00:37:52,368
He didn't show up in the graduation ceremony

338
00:37:52,568 --> 00:37:55,705
What's wrong with him
He left with no words

339
00:38:01,319 --> 00:38:01,959
Ye Zi

340
00:38:02,159 --> 00:38:03,164
Here

341
00:38:03,364 --> 00:38:08,002
You are looking for Xiang Zeyi

342
00:38:11,154 --> 00:38:13,778
He may contact you in a few days

343
00:38:13,978 --> 00:38:14,610
Right

344
00:38:14,810 --> 00:38:18,022
He may be preparing a surprise for us

345
00:38:18,222 --> 00:38:18,970
Don't worry

346
00:38:24,278 --> 00:38:27,063
I have some news

347
00:38:27,263 --> 00:38:31,854
The college said Xiang Zeyi dropped out of school

348
00:38:32,054 --> 00:38:33,066
What

349
00:38:33,266 --> 00:38:35,046
Where is he now

350
00:38:35,246 --> 00:38:36,704
Where is he

351
00:38:36,904 --> 00:38:38,576
Nobody sees him

352
00:38:38,776 --> 00:38:40,444
But it has been settled

353
00:38:40,644 --> 00:38:42,595
Xiang Zeyi dropped out of school by his own will

354
00:38:56,344 --> 00:38:58,955
Ye Zi

355
00:39:25,454 --> 00:39:27,861
Xiang Zeyi,you big liar

356
00:40:29,533 --> 00:40:31,228
I want an explanation

357
00:40:36,230 --> 00:40:38,252
As long as you tell me

358
00:40:38,452 --> 00:40:40,508
I will believe you

359
00:40:52,171 --> 00:40:52,746
Zeyi

360
00:40:56,993 --> 00:40:58,742
Just tell me

361
00:40:58,942 --> 00:41:02,493
Nothing

362
00:41:14,218 --> 00:41:17,220
It's just a simple request
And you can't meet

363
00:41:22,917 --> 00:41:23,634
OK

364
00:41:23,834 --> 00:41:26,843
Then I will not ask

365
00:41:27,043 --> 00:41:31,342
I've already waited for you for so many years

366
00:41:31,542 --> 00:41:37,898
I believe I will wait till the day you are willing to tell me the truth

367
00:41:58,349 --> 00:42:00,767
I'll be back soon Zhu Xuan

368
00:42:00,967 --> 00:42:02,454
Ye Zi,something happened to Xinyu

369
00:43:07,754 --> 00:43:14,293
I didn't have enough time to say goodbye to her
How could she leave so fast

370
00:43:14,493 --> 00:43:18,945
It's a changing world

371
00:43:19,145 --> 00:43:26,133
The person who we held yesterday may say goodbye to us today

372
00:43:26,333 --> 00:43:32,127
When we never experience the true leaving

373
00:43:32,327 --> 00:43:36,325
we may not perish what we have

374
00:43:36,525 --> 00:43:39,738
We always think what we have is not enough

375
00:43:39,938 --> 00:43:44,617
We always think there's still chance

376
00:43:44,817 --> 00:43:47,613
to hear his heartbeat

377
00:43:47,813 --> 00:43:52,861
to say goodbye when being apart

378
00:43:53,061 --> 00:43:56,224
Till the last

379
00:43:56,424 --> 00:43:58,082
We realize

380
00:43:58,282 --> 00:44:03,907
There's no goodbye for truly leaving

381
00:44:04,107 --> 00:44:08,301
All we can do

382
00:44:08,501 --> 00:44:14,671
is to accept every goodbye before it's too late

383
00:44:14,871 --> 00:44:17,496
And move on strongly
